Steps to Run the Application:

1) first run the npm start command on both the directories
2) then on your MongoDB Compass connect with teh localhost port # 27017
3) Install the extension "MongoDB for VS Code" and connect it as well 
4) Run the command "node index.js" for the backend
5) Run the command  "npm start" to run teh application on browser


the dependency Cors is used to handle the application running on different ports the backend is running on port 5000 and 
frontend is running on port 3000.
